Question: How did you find participating in this experiment? Please tell us anything you'd like to share about your experience.
Response: I found this to be an interesting and insightful experience. It was interesting testing my instincts to english words vs english looking jibberish, and I must admit, I think I even made a few mistakes realising perhaps that that actually was a word after all when I deemed it jibberish. The comprehension was interesting as well as I did indeed find my mind to wander sometimes, perhaps this was due to my stress levels and other things on my mind. My only suggestion which I would've liked to have done would be to have the option to share my thoughts when I found my mind wandering, but I assume that specific data was not necessary for the study. All in all I would rate this a very interesting and positive experience, thank you Amelia.
